Package com.onenetwork.backchain.client

Java client for interacting with One Network's Backchain.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BackchainClientConfig
    Marker interface for capturing the configuration needed to connect to a particular Backchain implementation.
    ContentBackchainClient
    Interface for interacting with the ContentBackchain.
    DisputeBackchainClient
    Interface for interacting with the DisputeBackchain.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BackchainClientFactory
    Factory for acquiring instances of ContentBackchainClient and DisputeBackchainClient.
    Dispute
    A Dispute captures a concern raised by a Backchain participant about a transaction or business transaction.
    Dispute.DisputeFilter
    Object used for querying Disputes.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Dispute.Reason
    Describes all reason code for which a Dispute may be filed.
    Dispute.State
    Describes all possible states in the lifecycle of the Dispute.

Package com.onenetwork.backchain.client Description

Java client for interacting with One Network's Backchain.

See the onechain-back-client github project for more details.
